<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Benz Teufel zu Neumarkt in der Oberpfalz</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen des geforderten Sicherns Unkenntnis über die Betroffenen mit und gewährt dem Adressaten bis Jakobstag vier Tage Geleit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_121" id="59v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_121_r2l24">Bencʒen teẅffel <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Neẅnmarkt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="margınleft"><ab facs="#facs_121_r1l2">Jn bapıro </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l25">Bencʒ teẅfel als du vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt von rede <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe an dıch komen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l26">ſey . daʒ wır dıch für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſıcher <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l27">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu haſt du vns nıht benennet welh dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das an = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l28">treffe daʒ wır darcʒu nıht <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wenn du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l29"><expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſand Jacobs tag ſchıerıſt ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wılt . ſo ſolt du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r2l30">ʒu vnd von vns . für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geuerd vnd bey vns für </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_122" id="60r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_122_r2l1"><expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vıer tag geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / alſdenn <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dein rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_122_r2l2"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo Erhardȷ Schürſtab <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_122_r2l3"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_121" id="59v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Benczen Tewffel <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Newnmarkt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">In bapiro. </note>
</app>Bencz Tewfel, als du uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast von
                        rede <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die an dich komen sey, daz wir dich für
                        uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sicher
                            <expan>sölte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu hast du uns niht benennet, welh
                        die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das antreffe, daz wir darczu niht
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>;
                        wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wenn du
                            <expan>hiezwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Jacobs tag schierist</q>25.07.1420</note>
</app> zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wilt, so solt du zu und von uns
                        für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geverd und bey uns für <pb facs="#facs_122" id="60r"/>
<expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vier tag geleyt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, alsdenn
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dein rede
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo Erhardi Schürstab
                                <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex>.</expan>
</ab></div>
</div></body>
